If you have access to git:

Installation:
	git clone https://github.com/Jesin/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the ~/.vim directory, and fetch submodules:
	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update


If you only have access to svn:

Installation:
	svn co https://github.com/Jesin/dotvim.git/trunk ~/.vim

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the ~/.vim directory, and update the full file tree:
	cd ~/.vim
	svn up
